{"tid":1308374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] 中英聯合聲明超級懶人包 Video","createTime":"2019-07-12T01:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T14:15:29.000Z","uid":1806,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a0a7b7e4053e1858fc77adb1d9ca230fd2a55d","tid":1308374,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:16:15.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;中英聯合聲明&ldquo; 相信每一位香港人都聽過依6隻字，而近期開始多人提起, 咁究竟依一份聲明既內容係講乜野呢？<br />\n<br />\n英國同中國兩個國家一直對依份聲明有無效仲一直爭論緊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而今次逃犯修訂條例如果通過，就會摧毀依份聲明入面提過的承諾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過依個超級懶人包短片將中英聯合聲明，由巴絲聲音導航，精簡咁帶<br />\n出裡面既內容，幫助各位了解而家既情況。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得有用, 請幫推POST同share俾身邊既人了解啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再大家要記住當日大家曾經講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>兄弟爬山 各有各做 齊上齊落<br />\n不受傷 不被捕 不分化 不割席 不督灰 不撤不散</strong><br />\n<br />\nCredit to:<br />\nBackground Music from YouTube Audio Library<br />\nPictures: 反送中文宣谷Channel 文宣巴絲制作<br />\n<br />\n幫其他巴絲Forward link:<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>【任務欄】<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306215</a><br />\n任務眾多，請自行因應人數及背後目的考慮做邊D任 ；黃色為主線任務；紅色係Boss <br />\n7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0BR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=0b3a162a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0BR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=cb02ad2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_bl